<h2 id="from-zero-to-todos">From Zero to Todos</h2>
<h3 id="install-the-generator">Install the generator</h3>
<pre><code class="lang-sh">$ npm install -g yo generator-thorax</code></pre>
<h3 id="generate-your-application">Generate your application</h3>
<pre><code class="lang-sh">$ yo thorax todo-list
